於2005年估計牠們的數量有1,220,000隻，及600,853繁殖對。當中的402,571對是在福克蘭群島；72,102對在南喬治亞島；120,171對在[[智利|智利]]；600對在赫德島；其餘的則有5,409對<ref name="Robertson2007">{{cite journal|last1=Robertson|first1=G.|last2=Moreno|first2=C. A.|last3=Lawton|first3=K.|last4=Arata|first4=J.|last5=Valencia|first5=J.|last6=Kirkwood|first6=R.|year=2007|title=An estimate of the population sizes of Black-browed (''Thalassarche melanophrys'') and Grey-headed (''T. chrysostoma'') Albatross breeding in the Diego Ramírez Archipelago, Chile|journal=Emu|issue=107|pages=239–244}}</ref><ref name="Huin">{{cite web|url=http://www.falklandsconservation.com/wildlife/birds/AlbatrossCensusReport05-06.pdf|title=Census of the Black-browed Albatross population of the Falkland Islands, 2000 and 2005|accessdate=2009-02-23|last1=Huin|first=N.|last2=Reid|first2=T.|format=pdf|publisher=Falklands Conservation|10=|date=2007年4月|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110410045511/http://www.falklandsconservation.com/wildlife/birds/AlbatrossCensusReport05-06.pdf|archivedate=2011-04-10}}</ref><ref name="Poncet">{{cite journal|last1=Poncet|first1= S.|last2=Robertson|first2= G.|last3=Phillips|first3=R. A.|last4=Lawton|first4=K.|last5=Phalan |first5=B.|last6=Trathan|first6=P. N.|last7=Croxall|first7=J. P.|year=2006|title=Status and distribution of wandering Black-browed and Grey-headed Albatrosses breeding at South Georgia|journal=Polar Biology|issue=29|pages=772–81}}</ref>。

牠們喜歡在[[大陸架|大陸架]]上覓食。福克蘭群島的群落會飛到近[[巴塔哥尼亞架|巴塔哥尼亞架]]（Patagonian Shelf）過冬；南喬治亞島的群落則會到[[南非|南非]]海域利用[[本格拉寒流|本格拉寒流]]來覓食；智利的群落會飛到巴塔哥尼亞架、[[智利架|智利架]]（Chilean Shelf）及遠至[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]過冬。牠們的最有可能在北大西洋出現的[[信天翁|信天翁]]。在[[美國本土|美國本土]]就約有20個觀察報告<ref name="Dunn">{{cite book|last1=Dunn|first1=Jon L.|last2=Alderfer|first2=Jonathan|editor1-first=Barbara|editor1-last=Levitt|title=National Geographic Field Guide to the Birds of North America|url=https://archive.org/details/nationalgeograph0000unse_z1a7|edition=fifth|year=2006|publisher=National Geographic Society|location=Washington D.C.|isbn=978 0 7922 5314 3|page=[https://archive.org/details/nationalgeograph0000unse_z1a7/page/80 80]|chapter=Albatrosses}}</ref>。

==行為==
黑眉信天翁群落非常嘈吵，經常發聲來劃定自己的地盤。牠們會利用尾巴來示愛<ref name="Robertson2003"/>。

===覓食===
黑眉信天翁吃[[魚類|魚類]]、[[烏賊|烏賊]]、[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]、[[屍體|屍體]]及漁業的丟棄物<ref name="Cherel">{{cite journal|last1=Cherel|first1=Y.|last2=Weimerskirch|first2=H.|last3=Trouve|first3=C.|year=2002|title=Dietary evidence for spatial foraging segregation in sympatric albatrosses (''Diomedea spp.'') rearing chicks at Iles Nuageuses, Kerguelen|journal=Marine Biology|issue=141|pages=1117–29}}</ref><ref name="Xavier">{{cite journal|last1=Xavier|first1=J. C.|last2=Croxall|first2=J. P.|last3=Trathan|first3=P. N.|last4=Wood|first4=A. G.|year=2003|title=Feeding strategies and diets of breeding grey-headed and wandering albatrosses at South Georgia|journal=Marine Biology|issue=143|pages=221–32}}</ref><ref name="Arata">{{cite journal|last1=Arata|first1=J.|last2=Robertson|first2=G.|last3=Valencia|first3=J.|last4=Lawton|first4=K|year=2003|title=The Evangelistas Islets, Chile: a new breeding site for black-browed albatrosses|journal=Polar Biology|issue=26|pages=687–90}}</ref>。牠們也會從其他[[物種|物種]]中偷取食物<ref name="Robertson2003"/>。

===繁殖===
[[File:Thalassarche_melanophris_MHNT.jpg|thumb]]
黑眉信天翁一般會在長滿草叢的陡坡或峭壁上築巢。不過在[[福克蘭群島|福克蘭群島]]上，牠們卻會在岸邊的草坪上築巢<ref name="BLI"/>。牠們每年只會生產一次，約於9月至11月間，每次只會生一隻蛋。雙親都會協助孵化，孵化期約需68-71天。雛鳥出生後的120-130天就會換羽。幼鳥2-3歲大就會回到群落中，目的是示愛，到了10歲就可以[[繁殖|繁殖]]<ref name="Robertson2003"/>。

==保育==
[[Image:Black-browed-albatross-Colony.jpg|left]]的黑眉信天翁的群落。]]
[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]]基於黑眉信天翁的數量大幅下降而將之列為[[瀕危|瀕危]]。在近[[南喬治亞島|南喬治亞島]]的鳥島，牠們繁殖對的數量每年就減少4%<ref name="Poncet"/>，而在[[凱爾蓋朗群島|凱爾蓋朗群島]]的數量於1979年至1995年就減少了17%<ref name="Wei">{{cite book|last1=Weimerskirch|first1=H.|last2=Jouventin|first2=P.|editor1-first=G.|editor1-last=Robertson|editor2-last=Gales|editor2-first=R.|title=Albatross biology and conservation|year=1998|publisher=Surrey Beatty and Sons|location=Chipping Norton, Australia|pages=84–91|chapter=Changes in population sizes and demographic parameters of six albatross species breeding on the French sub-antarctic islands}}</ref>。在[[迭戈拉米雷斯群島|迭戈拉米雷斯群島]]的數量於1980年代就不斷下降，直到近年才有所回升<ref name="Schlatter">{{cite book|last1=Schlatter|first1=R. P.|editor1-first=J. P.|editor1-last=Croxall|editor2-first=P. G. H.|editor2-last=Evans|editor3-first=R. W.|editor3-last=Schreiber|title=Status and conservation of the world's seabirds|year=1984|publisher=International Council for Bird Preservation (Techn. Publ.)|location=Cambridge, U.K.|pages=261–9|chapter=The status and conservation of seabirds in Chile }}</ref><ref name="Arata1">{{cite journal|last1=Arata|first1=J.|last2=Moreno|first2=C. A.|year=2002|title=Progress report of Chilean research on albatross ecology and conservation|journal=Convention for the Conservation of Antarctic Marine Living Resources Working Group on Fish Stock Assessment}}</ref>。但在[[福克蘭群島|福克蘭群島]]的數量於1980年代則有所上升<ref name="Croxall"/><ref name="Gales">{{cite book|last1=Gales|first1=R.|editor1-first=G.|editor1-last=Robertson|editor2-first=R.|editor2-last=Gales|title=Albatross biology and conservation|year=1998|publisher=Surrey Beatty & Sons|location=Chipping Norton, Australia|chapter=Albatross populations: status and threats}}</ref>，可能是因大量漁業丟棄物所致<ref name="Thompson">{{cite journal|last1=Thompson|first1=K. R.|last2=Riddy|first2=M. D.|year=1995|title=Utilisation of offal discards from finfish trawlers around the Falkland Islands by the Black-browed Albatross Diomedea melanophris|journal=Ibis|issue=137|pages=198–206}}</ref>；不過近年當地的數量卻有大幅的下滑<ref name="Huin"/>。整體而言，牠們的數量在64年間大幅下降了67%<ref name="BLI"/>。

在南方[[海洋|海洋]]加劇使用[[延繩釣|延繩釣]]是令黑眉信天翁數量減少的主因<ref name="Prince">{{cite book|last1=Prince|first1=P. A.|last2=Croxall|first2=J. P.|last3=Trathan|first3=P. N.|last4=Wood|first4= A. G.|editor1-first=G.|editor1-last=Robertson|editor2-first=R.|editor2-last=Gales|title=Albatross biology and conservation|year=1998|publisher=Surrey Beatty & Sons|location=Chipping Norton, Australia|chapter=The pelagic distribtuion of South Georgia albatrosses and their relationships with fisheries}}</ref><ref name="Schiavini">{{cite book|last1=Schiavini|first1=A.|last2=Frere|first2=E.|last3=Gandini|first3=P.|last4=Garcia|first4=N.|last5=Crespo|first5=E.|editor1-first=G.|editor1-last=Robertson|editor2-first=R.|editor2-last=Gales|title=Albatross biology and conservation|year=1998|publisher=Surrey Beatty & Sons|location=Chipping Norton, Australia|pages=208–13|chapter=Albatross-fisheries interactions in Patagonian shelf waters}}</ref><ref name="Stagi">{{cite book|last1=Stagi|first1=A.|last2=Vaz-Ferreira|first2=R.|last3=Marin|first3=Y.|last4=Joseph|first4=L.|editor1-first=G.|editor1-last=Robertson |editor2-first=R.|editor2-last=Gales|title=Albatross biology and conservation|year=1998|publisher=Surrey Beatty & Sons|location=Chipping Norton, Australia|pages=220–4|chapter=The conservation of albatrosses in Uruguayan waters}}</ref><ref name="Tuck">{{cite journal|last1=Tuck|first1=G.|last2=Polacheck|first2=T.|year=1997|title=Trends in tuna long-line fisheries in the Southern Oceans and implications for seabird by-catch: 1997 update|issue=CCSBT-ERS/97|publisher=Division of Marine Research|location=Hobart, Australia}}</ref>。事實上，黑眉信天翁是最易被漁業所殺死<ref name="Schiavini"/><ref name="Stagi"/><ref name="Gales2">{{cite journal|last1=Gales|first1=R.|last2=Brothers|first2=N.|last3=Reid|first3=T.|year=1998|title=Seabird mortality in the Japanese tuna longline fishery around Australia, 1988-1995|journal=Biological Conservation|issue=86|pages=37–56}}</ref><ref name="Murray">{{cite journal|last1=Murray|first1=T. E.|last2=Bartle|first2=J. A.|last3=Kalish|first3=S. R.|last4=Taylor|first4=P. R.|year=1993|title=Incidental capture of seabirds by Japenese southern bluefin tuna longline vessels in New Zealand waters, 1988-1992|journal=bird conservationalist internationalbird conservationalist international|issue=3|pages=181–210}}</ref><ref name="Boix">{{cite journal|last1=Ryan|first1=P.G.|last2=Boix-Hinzen|first2=C.|year=1998|title=Tuna long-line fisheries off southern Africa: the need to limit seabird bycatch|journal=South African Journal of Science|issue=94|pages=179–182}}</ref><ref name="Ryan">{{cite journal|last1=Ryan|first1=P. G.|last2=Keith|first2=D.G.|last3=Kroese|first3=M.|year=2002|title=Seabird bycatch by tuna longline fisheries off southern Africa, 1998-2000|journal= South African Journal of Science|issue=24|page=103}}</ref><ref name="Reid2">{{cite journal|last1=Reid|first1=T. A.|last2= Sullivan|first2=B. J.|year=2004|title=Longliners, black-browed albatross mortality and bait scavenging in Falkland Island waters: what is the relationship?|journal=Polar Biology|issue=27|pages=131–9}}</ref>。另外，[[拖網捕漁|拖網捕漁]]也令黑眉信天翁的數量減少，特別是在[[巴塔哥尼亞架|巴塔哥尼亞架]]<ref name="Sullivan">{{cite journal|last1=Sullivan|first1=B.|last2=Reid|first2=T.|year=2002|title=Seabird interactions/mortality with longliners and trawlers in the Falkland/Malvinas Island waters|journal=Unpublished report|series=CCAMLR-WG-FSA-02/36}}</ref>及[[南非|南非]]附近<ref name="Watkins">{{cite journal|last1=Watkins|first1=B. P.|last2=Petersen|first2= S. L.|last3=Ryan|first3=P. G.|year=2007|title=Interactions between seabirds and deep-water hake trawl gear: an assessment of impacts in South African waters|journal=Biological Conservation|issue=DRAFT}}</ref>。

黑眉信天翁受到《[[波昂公約|波昂公約]]》及《[[信天翁及海燕保育公約|信天翁及海燕保育公約]]》的保護，其數量受到監察，而繁殖地也受到保護。[[赫德島|赫德島]]、[[麥克唐納群島|麥克唐納群島]]、[[麥誇里島|麥誇里島]]及[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]等都被列為[[世界遺產|世界遺產]]而獲得加以保護。

